zair author to buy pl 480 rice - usda zair ha been author to purcha about 30,000 tonn of u.s. rice under an exist pl 480 agreement , the u.s. agricultur depart said . it may buy the rice , valu at 5.5 mln dlr , between march 31 and august 31 , 1987 , and ship it from u.s. port by septemb 30 , the depart said . the purcha author cover the entir quantiti of rice provid under the agreement .